---
title: Hoisin Beef Stir Fry with Bok Choy, Snow Peas, and Bell Peppers
description: We’ve said it once and we’ll say it again: stir-frying is a great technique for getting dinner on the table quick! Today, we’re using a colorful medley of bell pepper, bok choy, and snow peas for crunch. Ginger, garlic, lemon, and hoisin create a sweet and sour sauce that you’ll be licking of the plate.
